In conclusion, I humbly request the court's leniency and understanding as I plead guilty to my involvement in this bribery case. While I fully acknowledge the seriousness of my actions, I believe that the verifiable information provided today demonstrates my sincere remorse, commitment to personal growth, and dedication to rectifying the harm caused. I am prepared to accept any consequences deemed appropriate and vow to use this experience as a catalyst for positive change in my life.

